line_1: Silver his buskins, and with gems o'erlaid;
line_2: Of burnish'd silver were his sandals made,

line_1: That weight of wood, with leathern coat o'erlaid;
line_2: Those ample clasps, of solid metal made;

line_1: Wi' babs o' red roses and breast-knots o'erlaid!
line_2: I' the kirk sic commotion last Sabbath she made,
